summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the improvement of S.W. Kenyon St. from 9th Ave. S.W. to approximately 130 feet east thereof and from approximately 130 feet west of 7th Ave. S.W. to 1st Ave. S. and certain other streets, avenues, alleys, and easements under Local Improvement District No. 6683, and making an appropriation from the Neighborhood Improvement Fund in aid thereof.
